Invocation Name: music bot
des:
MusicBot is an AI (Artificial Intelligence) musician that can compose music based on what you command! And, just like in a real live music bar... you can buy the virtual musician a virtual drink!

Sometimes guest musicians might show up - when you buy her a virtual drink, this is the skill for you!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
